				<wikidot:authorName>not_a_seagull</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3009022</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I keep saying &quot;why do people still make dado skips? The entire idea has been milked harder than a cow that lactates gold. Slapping dado on what would make a better standalone skip only hurts good ideas.&quot;</p> <p>This suffers from that somewhat. You could probably take dado’s name off of this skip, replace it with Joe the Anomalous Spider Fan, and it wouldn’t change much. That being said, the idea is sufficiently neat, and the dialogue, although a little hammy, puts a little spin on dado that I haven’t seen yet.</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
