						 <p>Gotta echo some of the aforementioned opinions. The idea of giant spiders acting like dogs is crazy and definitely caught my attention - I love it (as a person scared of both dogs and spiders). However the execution of the article fell a little flat. The log did not do anything much and the Instagram conversation did not bring anything new about dado except for their fear of spiders.</p> <p>I'm going to novote for now.</p> 
