					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13596652#post-4735042</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13596652/scp-5185#post-4735042</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 31 Jul 2020 17:24:12 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Professor_JD</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3774501</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Funnily enough I got a fright when I went into my kitchen and thought there was a mouse in the dark. Turn on light, it's a spider, not anomalously big, but way bigger than expected. No idea how it got into the house, my dog chased it around a bit. I managed to get one of its legs between a fork tong and flick it out the back door.</p> <p>So I relate to dado here and his fear of big spiders. Small ones I'm fine with, just when it's bigger than certain coins or has legs as long as pound notes, then I freak out XD. +1 From me for adding a little more personal flair to dado and his life. And for doing a fun spider SCP.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
